<i>In last week's episode of</i> Soap,

00:04.480 --> 00:08.109
<i>Elaine told Danny that if he tried</i>
<i>to put an end to their relationship</i>

00:08.320 --> 00:10.676
<i>she would have her father</i>
<i>put an end to Danny.</i>

00:11.000 --> 00:13.595
<i>Burt ended up agreeing</i>
<i>to go to an institution,</i>

00:13.800 --> 00:16.599
<i>where he can hopefully</i>
<i>put an end to his invisibility.</i>

