<i>once invested and lost</i>
<i>$40,000 with Chester.</i>

00:26.320 --> 00:27.320
<i>Confused?</i>

00:27.480 --> 00:30.552
<i>You won't be</i>
<i>after this week's episode of</i> Soap.

00:30.760 --> 00:32.717
[♪♪♪]

